Here are my thoughts to make this a more spectacular salad the kids love. I added two cups of chopped english cucumber (one whole cucumber, peeled); add 1/4 cup chopped fresh mint; Also, I used kidney beans rather than pinto. This is great when paired with the "Rotini and Black Bean Salad" (with the changes I made to it under the reviews).

